							</svg>
						</div>
						<div class="w-8 h-8 bg-teal-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-semibold text-sm mb-3 mx-auto">4</div>
						<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Download Result</h4>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Preview and download the merged video</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Content Section for SEO with Sidebar -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-16 px-4 md:px-6">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
					<!-- Main Content -->
					<div class="lg:col-span-3">
				<!-- Introduction -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Merge Videos Online - Fast & Easy</h2>
					<div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-gray-700 space-y-4">
						<p>
							Need to combine multiple video clips into one seamless file? Whether you're merging presentation segments, combining footage from different sources, or creating a longer video from shorter clips, complex video editing software often feels like overkill.
						</p>
						<p>
							Our video merger lets you upload multiple files, arrange them in any order, set custom durations, and download a single merged video. No complicated timelines, no steep learning curves. Your videos are processed entirely in your browser, keeping your content private and secure.
						</p>
						<p>
							Drag, drop, arrange, and merge. It's that simple. Because combining videos shouldn't require a degree in video editing.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- How It Works -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">How to Merge Videos Online</h3>
					<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Multi-File Upload</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								Upload multiple video files at once or add them one by one. Supports MP4, WebM, MOV, and MKV.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Drag & Drop Ordering</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								Easily reorder your clips by dragging and dropping. See your changes in real-time with instant visual feedback.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Custom Duration Control</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								Set custom durations for each clip. Videos longer than the set duration will loop seamlessly to fill the time.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div>
							<h4 class="text-lg font-medium text-gray-900 mb-3">Seamless Preview</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
								Preview your merged video before processing. Watch clips play sequentially to ensure perfect timing and order.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- Why Choose This Tool -->
				<div class="mb-16">
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-6">Why Merge Videos With Our Tool?</h3>
					<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-8 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
						<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600">
										<path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.62,11.38L9,14.77L18.88,4.88L21.71,7.71L9,20.42Z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Completely Free</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">No watermarks, no time limits, no hidden costs.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600">
										<path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.62,11.38L9,14.77L18.88,4.88L21.71,7.71L9,20.42Z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Privacy First</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">All processing happens locally. Your videos never leave your device.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600">
										<path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.62,11.38L9,14.77L18.88,4.88L21.71,7.71L9,20.42Z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Smart Resizing</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Automatically resizes all videos to match the first one or set global dimensions.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600">
										<path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.62,11.38L9,14.77L18.88,4.88L21.71,7.71L9,20.42Z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Universal Compatibility</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Works with all major video formats and on any modern device.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600">
										<path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.62,11.38L9,14.77L18.88,4.88L21.71,7.71L9,20.42Z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">No Installation</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Works instantly in your browser. No software to download or install.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
							<div class="flex items-start gap-3">
								<div class="w-6 h-6 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-green-600">
										<path d="M9,20.42L2.79,14.21L5.62,11.38L9,14.77L18.88,4.88L21.71,7.71L9,20.42Z"/>
									</svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<h4 class="font-medium text-gray-900 mb-1">Flexible Duration</h4>
									<p class="text-sm text-gray-600">Set any duration for each clip with automatic looping when needed.</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<!-- FAQ Section -->
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
					<div class="space-y-6">
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">How many videos can I merge at once?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">There's no hard limit on the number of videos you can merge. The only constraint is your device's available memory and processing power.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What happens if my videos have different resolutions?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">By default, all videos are resized to match the dimensions of the first video you upload. You can also set custom global dimensions if needed.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I loop shorter videos to match longer ones?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Yes! Set a custom duration for any clip, and if it's shorter than the duration you specify, it will loop seamlessly to fill the time.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Is the tool free to use?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Absolutely! Our video merger is completely free with no watermarks, time limits, or hidden costs. Use it as much as you need.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Are my videos private and secure?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Yes, completely. All video processing happens locally in your browser using WebAssembly. Your videos never get uploaded to our servers.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">What video formats are supported?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">We support MP4, WebM, MOV, and MKV. If your browser can play it, chances are we can merge it.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I preview the merged video before downloading?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">Yes! The preview player will play through all your clips in order so you can see exactly how the final merged video will look.</p>
						</div>
						
						<div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-200">
							<h4 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Does merging videos reduce quality?</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-600">We use efficient encoding to maintain the best possible quality while keeping file sizes reasonable. The output quality will be very close to your original videos.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
					</div>
					
					<!-- Sidebar -->
					<RecommendedTools currentToolId="merge" category="video-editing" />
				</div>
			</div>
